h=1080&amp;height=1568\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/80235ba56fed29a7e7d04.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1568\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/80235ba56fed29a7e7d04.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1568\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGEyYjM3ODY2NDQ1OWQ0OGFjOTY3LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yNDEy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4a2b378664459d48ac967.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2412\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4a2b378664459d48ac967.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2412\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4a2b378664459d48ac967.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2412\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGRlN2Y2YjQ5NjNmYWNkNzVlYmU5LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yNDEy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4de7f6b4963facd75ebe9.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2412\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4de7f6b4963facd75ebe9.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2412\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4de7f6b4963facd75ebe9.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2412\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<b><div class=\"ab-player\"><div class=\"ab-video\"><video controls=\"\" preload=\"metadata\" src=\"https://pomf2.lain.la/f/l8g64yjt.mp4\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></video> </div></div></b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>大致过程：公主和驸马爷在西藏自驾游时出车祸，挺惨烈的样子。被好心人暂且救下，小姑紧急电话给上海卫健委，组织动员了公务员，消防员，民警和部队官兵来献血，公主整个人大换血两次，活了下来。然后被爸爸包机直飞四川华西医院，但人受伤还是挺严重的（医院诊断有30多个项目），躺医院几个月吃流食。（感谢纠正，已修改。公主是先在西藏阿里被紧急动员“输血”，然后再包机回四川华西的。）</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>众人感叹这家人的实力也太深厚了，惹不起。原来我们不仅是随时待割的韭菜，还是权贵的移动血包。</b> </div>",
